    <title>Hello there!</title>
    <link>https://socialhub.activitypub.rocks/t/hello-there/1340</link>
    <description>Hi everyone! 

I thought it would be a good thing to come here and say &quot;hi&quot; since 2021 will be the year where I&#39;ll be going more deeper in the ActivityPub space. :slight_smile: 

I have developed some tools around Mastodon API in the past, the most notable might be the multi-accounts focused client app [Sengi](https://nicolasconstant.github.io/sengi/). 

Currently I&#39;m developing a pet-project on ActivityPub to understand a bit more how all this is working. It&#39;s just a stupid Twitter2ActivityPub relay. The code is awful but it&#39;s functional, I have a [live instance here](https://beta.birdsite.live/) and the code is linked in the page (can&#39;t post more than 2 links as a new user). 
I will refine and refactor the code during the following weeks so that I&#39;ll have a healthy base to work from. 

My aim is to develop some more ambitious and useful tools in the close future, since ActivityPub can support ideas I had since some years already. I will try to develop my vision first in the first half of 2021 and will work on it concretely just after.
But one step at the time, for now I&#39;m the stupid padawan here to make a lot of errors and hopefully to learn from it. :no_mouth:

See you around!</description>
    
